reviewText: Se la pudiera devolver la devolva. Muy fresca y con malas palabras. Pensaba q era parecida a Sankybpakky
You need more new Puerto Rican movies.
Tremenda pelicula..yo la vi en el cine y decidi comprarla de regalo de navidad ara mi hermano para que se mate de la risa

OK so first off,
  This movie IS NOT FOR CHILDREN. ADULT and Teenager ONLY.

LOTS of offensive language and scenes.
BUT THE MOVIE IS JUST A BLAST.

By far one of the most funny/quierky/perverted(in a good way) movies I have seen in long time.
If you like movies like Sex Drive/American Pie/Porkys/Revenge of the nerds, You will like this.

Don't get me wrong, this movie is not a Hollywood movie, its a CHEAP movie made with virtually no FX at all, but the movie is just so much fun to watch with friends.
Give it a try, you will laugh so hard it will hurt! TRUST me it happen to all my friends!

Oh by the way... The DVD is no HD quality and ITS ONLY IN SPANISH.
But if you speak Spanish you will like it. ALOT!
